#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:17
msgid "Server Management"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can connect to multiple Mattermost servers from a single interface on"
" the desktop app. Servers appear as separate tabs while you are using the"
" app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:21
msgid "The Server Management section allows you to add, edit, and remove servers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:24
msgid "Adding Servers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:26
msgid "To access a new server from your desktop app environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:28
#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:46
#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:56
msgid "On the menu bar, go to **File > Settings**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:29
msgid "In the *Server Management* section, click **Add new server**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:30
msgid "In the **Name** field, enter the name that you want for the tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:31
msgid ""
"In the **URL** field, enter the complete URL of the server that you want "
"to connect to. Must begin with either ``http://`` or ``https://``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:32
#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:39
msgid "Click **Add**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:34
msgid "To access a new server from your Mac desktop app environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:36
msgid "On the menu bar, go to **Mattermost > Sign into Another Server**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:37
msgid ""
"In the **Server Display Name** field, enter the name that you want for "
"the tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the **Server URL** field, enter the complete URL of the server that "
"you want to connect to. Must begin with either ``http://`` or "
"``https://``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:42
msgid "Editing Servers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:44
msgid "To edit a server in your desktop app environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:47
msgid "Next to the server you want to update, click **Edit**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:48
msgid "Edit **Name** and/or **URL**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:49
msgid "Click **Save**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:52
msgid "Removing Servers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:54
msgid "To remove a server from your desktop app environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:57
msgid "Next to the server or team that you want to remove, click **Remove**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:58
msgid "Click **Remove**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:61
msgid "App Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:63
msgid ""
"In addition to `Mattermost Account Settings "
"<https://docs.mattermost.com/help/settings/account-settings.html>`__ , "
"the desktop app provides additional options to customize your experience."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:65
msgid ""
"The options appear in the Settings page, available from the **File > "
"Settings** or by CTRL/CMD+COMMA."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:70
msgid "Start app on login (Windows, Linux only)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:68
msgid ""
"When enabled, Mattermost application starts when you log in to your "
"machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:70
#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:75
#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:80
msgid "This setting is enabled by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:75
msgid "Check spelling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:73
msgid ""
"Highlight misspelled words in your messages. Available for English, "
"French, German, Spanish, and Dutch. To change the spelling language, "
"right-click inside a message box and navigate to **Spelling Languages** "
"in the context menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:80
msgid ""
"Show red badge on taskbar icon to indicate unread messages (Windows, Mac "
"only)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:78
msgid ""
"When enabled, a red badge is shown on the taskbar icon for unread "
"messages with a number count indicating unread mentions or direct "
"messages. If disabled, a red badge is only shown for unread mentions "
"(with a number count)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:85
msgid "Flash taskbar icon when a new message is received (Windows, Linux only)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/apps/desktop-guide.rst:83
msgid ""
"Configure whether the taskbar icon flashes for a few messages when a new "
"message is received on any of your active teams and servers."
msgstr ""

